{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id62e73ca5-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t25/s5327"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5327"},"text":"§ 5327.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Department of the Interior: availability of funds for Indian self-determination or self-governance contract or grant support costs","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Notwithstanding any other provision of law, including but not limited to the Indian Self-Determination Act of 1975, as amended [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t25/s5321"},"text":"25 U.S.C. 5321","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], on and after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1999-11-29"},"text":"November 29, 1999","children":[],"tail":", funds available to the Department of the Interior for Indian self-determination or self-governance contract or grant support costs may be expended only for costs directly attributable to contracts, grants and compacts pursuant to the Indian Self-Determination Act of 1975 and on and after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1999-11-29"},"text":"November 29, 1999","children":[],"tail":", funds appropriated in this title "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002264"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002264"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" shall not be available for any contract support costs or indirect costs associated with any contract, grant, cooperative agreement, self-governance compact or funding agreement entered into between an Indian tribe or tribal organization and any entity other than an agency of the Department of the Interior."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id62e73ca6-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/113/dB/s1000/a/3/tI/s113"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–113, div. B, § 1000(a)(3) [title I, § 113]","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1999-11-29"},"text":"Nov. 29, 1999","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/113/1535"},"text":"113 Stat. 1535","children":[],"tail":", 1501A–157.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id62e73ca7-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id62e73ca8-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id62e73ca9-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Indian Self-Determination Act of 1975, referred to in text, probably means the Indian Self-Determination Act, title I of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/638"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–638","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-04"},"text":"Jan. 4, 1975","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/2206"},"text":"88 Stat. 2206","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to this subchapter (§ 5321 et seq.). For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t25/s5301"},"text":"section 5301 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This title, referred to in text, is title I of the Department of the Interior and Related Agencies Appropriations Act, 2000, as enacted by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/113/dB/s1000/a/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–113, div. B, § 1000(a)(3)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1999-11-29"},"text":"Nov. 29, 1999","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/113/1535"},"text":"113 Stat. 1535","children":[],"tail":", 1501A–135. For complete classification of this title to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id62e73caa-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of the Department of the Interior and Related Agencies Appropriations Act, 2000, and not as part of the Indian Self-Determination and Education Assistance Act which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was formerly classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t25/s450j–3"},"text":"section 450j–3 of this title","children":[],"tail":" prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id62e73cab-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"similarProvisions","id":"id62e73cac-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Similar Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Similar provisions were contained in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/277/dA/s101/e/tI/s114"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–277, div. A, § 101(e) [title I, § 114]","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-10-21"},"text":"Oct. 21, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/2681-231"},"text":"112 Stat. 2681–231","children":[],"tail":", 2681–255."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
